name: Noble Fate, Mahitra
description: Increases own Crit DMG by 10% and DEF Penetration by 100. Upon dealing DMG to an enemy 500 times, increases all effects by x2.

name: Crystallized Technomagic, Rascal
description: Every 1.5 sec, gains 1 stack of Charge and recovers 1% mana.

name: Clear Blue Sky, Sherrkyle
description: Every 10 sec, marks Judgment Sigil on 1 random enemy for 15 sec, then deals M.DMG equal to 200% of ATK. Ignores DEF if the target is not a Hero.

name: Brilliant Praise, Brauxio
description: Upon using a Skill 3 times, creates a shield that blocks DMG equal to 200% of own ATK and increases own ATK by 20% for 10 sec. While the shield is active, gains immunity to CC.

name: Solar Halo, Ignisius
description: Attacking the enemy with 5 normal attacks increases M.DMG the target takes by 20% for 10 sec, and inflicts Stun for 0.5 sec. The M.DMG Boost effect is irremovable.

name: God's Book, Genesis
description: Increases the casting speed of all skills, and upon every skill use, increases ATK by 2% and DEF by 2% for all allies. This effect can stack up to 7 times.

name: Kiln of Futility, Targarios
description: Every 10 sec, increases own ATK by 10%, all DEF by 10%, and reduces Cooldown of all Skills by 1 sec. While in [Battle Initiation], Cooldown Reduction will be doubled. The ATK and DEF boost can be stacked up to max 4 times and is irremovable.

name: Might of the God King, Tyrannicus
description: Depending on which form Cain is in, Normal and Skill attacks grant additional effects. [God King] Stuns the target for 1 sec with a 20% chance. [Tyrant] Increases P.DMG the target takes by 20% for 5 sec. The target inflicted with this effect will not receive this effect again for 3 sec.

name: Aurelian Whisper, Goldbreeze
description: Skill hits increase M.DMG that the target takes by 10% for 10 sec. Every 8 sec, heals the ally with the lowest HP by 200% of own ATK and dispels all negative effects from the ally.

name: Supersonic Tempest, Gigantix
description: Increases ATK Spd by 100. Normal and Skill attacks grant a stack of Explosion on self and have a 3% chance of stunning the target for 4 sec. Upon gaining 100 Explosion stacks, Gigantix explodes, increasing ATK Spd and All Dodge Chance by 100. This effect is irremovable.

name: Blood Lancer Monolith
description: Increases own Crit DMG by 20%. Upon auto attack, deals P.DMG equal to 30% of ATK with [Flame of Monolith] and recovers HP equal to 20% of DMG dealt. When [Remove Limit] is active, the effect of [Flame of Monolith] is doubled.

name: Prism Nova, Arc Lumineir
description: Upon gaining Lights, receives various effects. Red Light - Increases ATK of all allies by 10% for 10 sec. Blue Light - Increases DEF of all allies by 10% for 10 sec. Green Light - Recovers Mana of all alies by 300.

name: The Guardian, Exian
description: After using own active Skill 3 times, increases all allies' P.DEF by 10% and ATK by 10% for 15 sec. ATK boost effect multiplies by 2 for the ally with the highest ATK.

name: Primal Flame, Flenos

description: [I'm the Adventure Guide!!] [Adventure Guide] becomes irremovable. Normal attacks have a 20% chance of reducing the target's Mana by 400 for the duration of Skill. This effect is activated only once every 3 sec.

name: Abyssal Breath
description: Increases DMG dealt to Non-Hero enemies of 2 allies with the highest ATK excluding self by 5% and heals HP of all allies equal to 2.5% of Max HP every 10 sec. When there is 1 enemy, increases Heal Rate by x2. This effect does not stack with effects from other allies.

name: Abyssal Crown
description: 30 sec after the battle starts, increases ATK of the ally with the highest ATK by 30%. This effect cannot be dispelled, and it does not stack with other effects for allies.

name: Abyssal Eye
description: Upon taking damage, deals M.DMG of 50% own ATK to the target and reduces ATK Spd of the target by 400 for 1.5 sec. After the ATK Spd Reduction Effect expires, the target is petrified for 2 sec. This effect will be activated only once every 30 sec.

name: Abyssal Nail Ornament
description: Upon attack, deals P.DMG equal to 4% of ATK that ignores DEF to the enemy every 0.5 sec for 10 sec. This effect will be activated once in 20 sec.

name: Academic Achievement Award
description: Increases ATK of all allies by 8%, and All DEF of self by 10%. This effect will not stack with other similar effects cast by allies.

name: Amethyst Pendulum
description: Increases All Crit Resistance by 200 for 7 sec every 10 sec.

name: Ancient God King's Coin
description: Increases ATK and Crit DMG by 20%.

name: Angry Pumpkin Head
description: All DMG taken is reduced by 10% and deal 10% more DMG to enemies.

name: Assassin's Veil
description: Increases P.Dodge by 100. Each successful dodge increases ATK by 1%, stacking up to max 20 times.

name: Belt Ornament of the Deep
description: At the beginning of the first battle, and every 30 sec, reduces DMG all allies take from enemies by 20% for 3 sec. This effect is irremovable and does not stack with effects from other allies. Each time the effect expires, dispels negative effects from all allies.

name: Blessing of Earth
description: When there is 1 enemy, ATK is boosted by 40%.

name: Book of the Mad
description: Every second, own Mana is reduced by 100, but own DMG to enemies is increased by 14%.

name: Burning Brazier of Elf
description: Upon attacking an enemy, there is a 10% chance to recover 1 MP.

name: Christmas Star Ornament
description: At the beginning of each battle, for 5 sec, increase Mana Recovery per sec by 260%. Also, Crit Resistance is increased by 100. This effect cannot be dispelled.

name: Christmas Tree of Holy Night
description: Crit DMG is increased by 50%.

name: Cooling Delicacy in the Summer
description: When the battle begins, reduces DMG from non-Hero enemies by 20% for 30 second(s), and recovers 100 MP every 2 second(s).

name: Cross Pumpkin Head
description: Max HP is increased by 20% and deal P.DMG worth 2% of Max HP to all nearby enemies within a small range.

name: Crystal Music Box
description: Increases DMG to Hero by 20% and takes 10% increased DMG.

name: Dice of Magical Letters
description: Upon attacking an enemy, deal 400% M. DMG for a 3% chance.

name: Drinking Horn of Ancient Cow
description: Upon auto attacking, there is a 10% chance that ATK rises by 10% and ATK Speed rises by 100.

name: Earth Core
description: ATK, HP and all DEF are increased by 10%.

name: Earth Fortress
description: When there is 1 enemy, reduces the target's Heal Rate by 10% and increases own DMG dealt to Bosses by 10%. This effect does not stack with effects from other allies.

name: Earth Protection
description: At the beginning of battle, gain CC immunity and a 50% boost to P. and M. DEF stats for 8 sec.

name: Earth Storm
description: When inflicted by CC, recovers Mana by 600 and gains [Earth Storm] for 10 sec, increasing all DMG nearby enemies take by 12% every sec.If activated in the Arena, [Earth Storm] deals P.DMG equal to 3% of the target's Max HP to nearby enemies every sec. This effect will not inflict a Crit Hit. The effect of [Earth Storm] has a Cooldown of 20 sec.

name: Fancy Traditional Pendant
description: Crit Chance is increased by 100 and Crit DMG is increased by 20%.

name: Fantastic Hybrid Animals
description: When the battle starts, increases DMG to Non-Hero enemies by 12% and takes 12% reduced DMG for 200 sec.

name: Feather of Sacrifice
description: For 120 sec after the battle starts, takes 10% extra DMG and increases all DMG taken by the enemy boss by 10%. This effect cannot be dispelled, and it does not stack with other effects for allies.

name: Forge Hammer MK-II
description: Normal attacks have a 5% chance to increase ATK Spd by 400 for 5sec.

name: Fragment of an Ancient Kingdom
description: Increases CC Resist by 200 and CC ACC by 200.

name: Frost Giant Mask
description: ATK upon Frost Giants increases by 40%, and DMG resistance against Frost Giants increases by 20%.

name: Goddess of Glory
description: Increases ATK Spd of 4 allies by 100 for 20 sec when the battle starts. This effect will not be stacked with other similar effects cast by allies.

name: Golden Apple of a Goddess
description: When the hero's HP falls below 25%, recover 30% of max HP and dispel all negative effects. Activates 1 time only.

name: Golden Cat Statue
description: Every Battle, Spd increases by 400 for the first 15 secs.

name: Golden Mask of Ancient King
description: Upon taking a hit, there is a 5% chance to gain invulnerability to all DMG for 3 sec. Has a cooldown of 5 sec.

name: Guardian Crystal of the Deep
description: When there is 1 enemy, all DEF is increased by 50%.

name: Happy Pumpkin Head
description: Every 7 sec, increases Heal Rate by 2% and heals HP by 100% of own ATK. Heal rate increase can be stacked up to max 15 times and cannot be removed.

name: Heart Cotton Candy
description: When the battle starts, increases ATK of self and the ally with the highest ATK by 10% for 20 sec. This effect will not stack with other similar effects cast by allies.

name: Heart of the Abyss
description: At the beginning of every battle, increases ATK of the ally with the highest ATK by 8% and reduces ATK of the enemy with the highest ATK by 15% for 100 sec. The ATK Boost effect can be stacked up to max 5 times, and all effects are irremovable.

name: Infernal Bond
description: At the start of every battle, increases all skill cooldown by 2.5 sec of one random enemy.

name: Infernal Gate
description: Increases All DEF by 10%, DMG dealt to enemies by 6%, and DMG dealt to Non-Hero enemies by 6%.

name: Infernal Greatsword
description: Own heal rate decreases by 30%, while Penetration increases by 300 and Crit DMG increases by 30%.

name: Infernal Whip
description: Every 8 sec, attacks all enemies and deals 20% of ATK as M.DMG. Targets take 10% increased DMG for the next 5 sec. DMG boost effect increases by 0.4% with every activation, and can be stacked max 25 times. DMG boost effect cannot be used simultaneously with same effects of other allies.

name: Insignia of Iron Conviction
description: Every 50 times this character takes M.DMG, dispel all harmful effects and gain a shield worth 480% of ATK for 5 sec. While this shield is in effect, gain immunity to CC and DMG Stacking effects.

name: Judgment of Light Bracelet
description: ACC and CC ACC rise by 300.

name: Juno's Special Dessert
description: Upon taking a hit, there is a 20% chance to increase All DMG the target takes by 10% for 5 sec. This effect cannot be used with other similar effects cast by allies.

name: Juno's Special Vitality Stew
description: Upon normal attack, deals P.DMG equal to 200% of ATK over time for 5sec. This effect cannot be used with other similar effects cast by allies.

name: Kiddy Chick
description: ATK Spd is increased by 80.

name: Lion of Protection
description: Increases own P.DEF by 20%, and P.Block by 100.

name: LuLu's Necklace
description: When the battle starts, increases DMG to Non-Hero enemies by 20% for 30 sec, and recovers Mana by 200 every 5 sec.

name: Madame's Bronze Mirrors
description: Raises own M.Block Chance by 300, and M.DMG Reduction is increased by 100.

name: Magical Flute
description: Every 8 sec, increases ATK Spd of 2 random allies and the caster by 100 for 4 sec.

name: Mask of Dark Elf
description: ATK upon Dark Elves increase by 40%, and DMG resistance against Dark Elves increases by 20%.

name: Mask of Draconic
description: ATK upon Draconics increase by 40%, and DMG resistance against Draconics increase by 20%.

name: Mask of Goblin
description: ATK upon Goblins increase by 40%, and DMG resistance against Goblins increases by 20%.

name: Mask of Harpy
description: ATK upon Harpies increase by 40%, and DMG resistance against Harpies increases by 20%.

name: Mask of Lizardman
description: ATK upon Lizardmen increase by 40%, and DMG resistance against Lizardmen increase by 20%.

name: Mask of Orc
description: ATK upon Orcs increase by 40%, and DMG resistance against Orcs increases by 20%.

name: Master Chef’s Recipe Book
description: Increases self's All DEF by 10%, and Heal Rate by 10%.

name: Nail Ornament of the Deep
description: At the beginning of each battle, fixes self's DEF to 0 and increases DMG dealt to bosses by 20% for 200 sec. This effect is irremovable.

name: New Year's Fanfare
description: Increases ATK of 4 allies by 5% for 20 sec at the beginning of every battle. This effect will not stack with other similar effects cast by allies.

name: New Year's Fireworks
description: ATK is increased by 5% for 60 sec at the start of each battle.

name: New-Type Thruster
description: When inflicted by CC, reduces self's Cooldown of all Skills by 5 sec and recovers 500 Mana every sec for 3 sec. Has a Cooldown of 20 sec.

name: Orbs of Contract
description: Every 7 sec, increase M.DEF by 1% of ATK. This effect stacks up to 6 times.

name: Otherworldly Helm
description: Increases self's Max HP by 20%, and upon taking DMG 3 times, reduces [DMG dealt to Heroes] of self and 2 enemies with the highest ATK by 50% for 5sec. This effect is irremoveable and has a 30 sec Cooldown.

name: Otherworldly Radiance
description: At the beginning of the first battle, and every 15 sec, gains [Otherworldly Radiance] that lasts for 4 sec. If [Otherworldly Radiance] is still active after 4 sec, dispels negative effects from self and reduces All DMG taken by 20% for 4 sec, dispels positive effect from 2 random enemies, knocks them away for 3 sec, and reduces their Mana by 800. DMG Reduction effect is irremoveable.

name: Otherworldly Sword
description: Consumes 4% of self's current HP every sec and disables Lifesteal, but increases DMG dealt per sec by 0.5% and Crit DMG by 0.5%. DMG and Crit DMG Boost effect can be stacked up to max 50 times. This effect automatically deactivates when HP falls below 25%.

name: Pendulum of Fantasy
description: At the beginning of each battle, ATK is permanently increased by 10%. This effect stacks up to max 5 times, and is irremovable.

name: Perfume of the Queen
description: When inflicted by CC for 3 times, removes own Negative Effects, and increases ATK Spd by 500 and gains immunity to CC for 4 sec.

name: Pocket Watch of Ancient Civilization
description: Every 10 sec, reduce all cooldowns by 1 sec and increase ATK Spd by 80 for 5 sec.

name: Primer for the Heroes
description: When HP is 20% or below, increases ATK by 30%, and increases ATK Spd and All DMG Reduction by 300.

name: Pumpkin-Stuck Evil Spirit
description: Increases own Max HP by 20%. When there is 1 enemy, increases ATK of all allies by 20%. This effect will not stack with other similar effects cast by allies.

name: Ring of Spirit Morph
description: At the beginning of every battle, HP does not fall below 10% for 4 sec. If HP falls below 15% for the duration of Skill, DMG dealt to Heroes will be reduced by 70% for 5 sec. All effects are irremovable.

name: Roaring Tiger Statue
description: When Hero health falls below 35%, deal DMG equal to 100% of ATK to nearby enemies and knock them down. Targeted enemies lose 14% ATK and 140 ATK Speed for 10 sec. Has a cooldown of 30 sec.

name: Sealed Chain of Ancient God
description: Every 20 sec, cast Silence to a random enemy for 3 sec and remove positive effects.

name: Solar Stone
description: Deals P.DMG equal to 20% of ATK to nearby enemies in a circular range every second and decreases their Heal Rate by 30% for 5 sec.

name: Sorcerous Black Dagger
description: Upon auto-attacking, there is a 10% chance to reduce the enemy's mana by 600. Has a cooldown of 6 sec.

name: Soul Spring Water
description: At the beginning of each battle, recover 24% HP and 12% Mana.

name: Spellbound Ring of the Deep
description: Upon the start of a battle for 8 sec, limit 1 enemy's ATK Spd to 1000 and reduce ATK by 20%.

name: Surprised Pumpkin Head
description: When inflicted by CC, immediately recovers Mana by 12% and increases ATK Spd by 200 for 5 sec. This effect activates once every 30 sec.

name: Talismans of Resistance
description: Upon receiving a negative effect, removes all negative effects. Afterward, gains immunity to CC for 1 sec. Has a Cooldown of 20 sec.

name: Tarot Card of Loss
description: Reduces Crit Chance by 150 and increases ATK by 30%.

name: The Ancient Scope
description: When MP is at 100%, Crit Chance and ACC rise by 400 for 10 sec. Has a cooldown of 20 sec.

name: Tome of Black Magic
description: Every 10 sec, target a single enemy. Said enemy takes DMG that ignores DEF equal to 2% of current HP each second for 5 sec, and reduces Mana by 200. This skill is effective only in the Arena.

name: Treasure Hunt Capsule
description: At the beginning of every battle, immediately reduces Cooldown of self's all Skills by 1 sec and increases DMG dealt to non-Hero enemies by 1%. The DMG Boost against Non-Hero enemies can be stacked up to max 10 times and is irremovable. At 10 stacks, the Cooldown Reduction effect is doubled.

name: Trident of the Deep
description: Dealing DMG to enemies 100 times increases ATK by 30% and Crit Chance by 200 for 15 sec. This effect cannot be dispelled.

name: Undead Mask
description: Increases DMG to Undead by 40% and Resistance against Undead by 20%.

name: Vase of Sacrifice
description: Upon taking DMG 50 times, heals HP of 1 random ally by 200% of My ATK and increases the target's ATK by 30% for 10 seconds.

name: Warm Turkey Dish
description: Increases own Max HP by 10% and All Block Chance by 100.

name: Well-Done Turkey Roast
description: Every 15 sec, recover HP equal to 1% of Max HP for 3 sec.

name: Bladebound Faith, Ezaias
description: Upon every Skill use, heals own HP equal to 4% of Max HP over 4 sec. Normal and Skill attacks increase All DMG the hit target takes by 8% for 8 sec.

name: Heretical Rosary
description: [Light of Salvation] Increases the duration of Shield by 1.2 sec and Silence by 1 sec.

name: Flame of Benevolence
description: [Touch of the Goddess - Mercy] The target hit by [Touch of Mercy] takes 8% increased All DMG for 15 sec. [Touch of the Goddess - Embrace]. [Touch of Embrace] additionally increases the target's ATK Spd by 300.

name: Sculpture of Chaos
description: [Offering of Atonement] Increases the duration of Invincibility by 1 sec and the effect of preventing enemies from receiving positive effects by 1 sec. [Field of Atonement] additionally recovers allies' Mana by 160 and reduces enemies' Mana by 160 every 2 sec.

name: Picture Book About Laws of Chaos
description: [Baptism of the Goddess] Increases the number of the ally with the highest ATK by 1 and [Baptism of the Goddess] effect additionally increases DMG dealt to Non-Hero enemies of the ally with the highest ATK by 3%.

name: Honorary Trophy
description: Increases ATK by 25% and Crit Chance by 250.

name: Honorary Medal
description: Increases ATK, HP, and All DEF of all allies by 7.5%. This effect does not stack with same effects from other allies.

name: Hero's Plaque of Appreciation
description: Increases Max HP by 25%. 30 sec after the batle starts, increases Crit DMG of the ally with the highest ATK excluding self by 50%. This effects is irremovable and does not stack with same effects from other allies.

name: Dragon's Doomstone
description: Increases DMG dealt to Non-Hero enemies by 10% and takes 5% reduced DMG from them. If the target is a [Dragon], the effect is tripled.

name: Apocalypsion's Tear
description: When there is only 1 enemy or more than 5 enemies, increases ATK and Crit DMG of all allies by 12% and 24% respectively. This effect does not stack with other similar effects cast by allies.
